		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Famicom on PAL TV?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm planning on purchasing a japanese Famicom console, but I've learned that it only comes with a standard antenna-cable connection (sorry for possible poor english <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />), and using it on a PAL TV results in low-quality audio.
<br />Is it true? Anyone got experience with this?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
